{
  "stem": "521.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But before we went through the Polish-Hungarian border, we were told that every-- every clothing, every equipmen, anything what we had, and they think we cannot carry it with us, should be put it in one house.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, then the Hungarians when we left were looking after.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whatever they wanted, they could take.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were just walked away with-- with very, very little.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last written communication we received on June 25th, which was sent to me by my parents and my fiancee from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, let me read my father's letter in which he said, 'We are sending you two of our photographs' two photographs of ourselves and 'We are well.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are thinking a lot of you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Ebbe,' who is my fiancee, 'is talking about you all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She behaves very well.' He writes again, 'We are well.' And I shouldn't worry about them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And whether the-- the room in the ghetto-- they didn't say ghetto but, 'Where we live is fairly good.' And write about you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by that time, I was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this was written in June, June the 25th.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I got into the hospital on June the 6th on-- on-- on the Normandy-- on the same day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And now, my mother said exactly the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she says, 'We are just thinking [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] of you all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we are talking with your father and with your fiancee about you.'",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] and she is a meeting with other people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother wasn't really-- didn't have too many friends or acquaintances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think I'm going to drink some water someplace, which I don't find.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
